              <li>Referrals to licensed attorneys for legal filings and hearings</li>
              <li>Certificate of rehabilitation and pardon guidance</li>
              <li>Post-relief updates to background and screening providers</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="disclaimer">We are not a law firm and do not provide legal advice. Legal work is handled by partner attorneys where permitted.</p>
